  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to study the effect of different combinations of fenofibrate
      and metformin on the cluster of metabolic syndrome (MetS) biochemical abnormalities, and to
      determine the dose combination allowing normalization of MetS patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
